name: PSIworx
short_description: PSIworx is a collection of MATLAB files to analyze data from the PSI SuperHead Fast Fluorometer series (www.psi.cz). These fluorometers are used in limnology and oceanography research communities. The program retrieves parameters from both single- and multiple-turnover induction and relaxation. Results are returned in both text file and .mat format.
summary: Data processing for the PSI fluorometer
